buckaroos is just my job.

51:31.010 --> 51:34.275
So save your money for
your next entry fee, cowboy.

51:49.629 --> 51:51.620
You ever try calf ropin'?

51:56.002 --> 51:59.266
Do I look like I can afford
a fuckin' ropin' horse?

52:15.353 --> 52:17.082
Shouldn't we move
a little closer?

52:17.155 --> 52:20.886
