humped like a frog.

52:35.507 --> 52:37.975
So, where do you figure
the most pussy is at?

52:38.043 --> 52:39.704
Las Vegas or California?

52:39.778 --> 52:41.006
Hell, I don't know...

52:41.079 --> 52:44.014
but if you make it
between Montana and Wyoming,
I'd take Wyoming...

52:44.082 --> 52:47.916
Hey! You might
want to keep it down,
I got two little girls here.

52:47.986 --> 52:50.955
Fuck you. Asshole.

52:51.423 --> 52:54.551
Probably quit
givin' it to his wife
after his kids was born.

52:54.626 --> 52:57.094
You know what that's like.
Yeah.

52:59.864 --> 53:02.594
Ennis, let's move.
Let's just move, okay?

53:06.770 --> 53:08.397
Now, I don't want
any trouble from you.

53:08.472 --> 53:10.599
You need to shut your
slop-bucket mouths,
you hear me?

53:10.674 --> 53:12.437
You ought to listen
to your old lady, then.

53:12.509 --> 53:15.342
Is that right?
Yeah. Move somewhere else.

53:16.747 --> 53:20.080
What about it?
You wanna lose about half
your fuckin' teeth, huh?

53:20.150 --> 53:22.744
Not tonight, bud.
I'd sure rather not.

53:32.830 --> 53:33.660
<i>Here she comes,</i>
<i>ladies and gentlemen!</i>

53:35.099 --> 53:37.033
<i>Oh, boy, look at her fly!</i>

53:37.101 --> 53:40.036
<i>This is Lureen Newsome</i>
<i>from right here</i>
<i>in Childress, Texas!</i>

53:40.104 --> 53:43.301
<i>Come on, folks,</i>
<i>she's gotta hear it,</i>
<i>let's give her a big hand!</i>

53:43.374 --> 53:44.898
<i>She's turnin' on two!</i>

53:46.176 --> 53:47.803
<i>She's around three!</i>

53:47.878 --> 53:50.642
<i>Come on, folks!</i>
<i>Help her home!</i>

53:50.714 --> 53:53.148
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

53:53.217 --> 53:57.051
<i>And the time is 16 and 9!</i>

54:00.591 --> 54:04.960
<i>Here's Cheyenne Hodson</i>
<i>from Cody, Wyoming!</i>

54:06.163 --> 54:07.653
<i>Come on, girl!</i>

54:10.034 --> 54:12.002
<i>She's headed around two!</i>

54:12.169 --> 54:14.831
<i>Is there anybody here</i>
<i>from Wyoming?</i>
Ma'am.

54:14.905 --> 54:16.633
<i>How about it, folks?</i>

54:19.609 --> 54:21.600
<i>Come on, Cheyenne!</i>

54:21.678 --> 54:25.546
<i>And her time is 17 and 2!</i>

54:27.984 --> 54:30.544
<i>Here comes Scotty Griffiths,</i>
<i>out of Lubbock, Texas.</i>

54:30.620 --> 54:32.178
<i>Come on, Scotty!</i>

54:32.322 --> 54:35.689
<i>Damn it!</i>
<i>Let's give Scotty Griffiths</i>
<i>a big hand, folks.</i>

54:35.925 --> 54:37.893
<i>Better luck next time,</i>
<i>cowboy.</i>

54:37.960 --> 54:41.020
<i>Boy, I tell you, folks,</i>
<i>what a heck of a way</i>
<i>to make a living!</i>

54:41.097 --> 54:43.065
<i>Next up is an up-and-comer!</i>

54:43.166 --> 54:48.069
<i>Jack Twist from</i>
<i>all the way up</i>
<i>in Lightning Flat, Wyoming.</i>

54:48.338 --> 54:52.775
<i>He's onboard Sleepy today!</i>
<i>Let's hope he's not!</i>

54:52.942 --> 54:53.931
<i>Okay!</i>

54:54.110 --> 54:58.171
<i>There they go, folks!</i>
<i>And look at Sleepy go, boy!</i>

54:58.247 --> 55:02.877
<i>He's broke free today, folks!</i>
<i>Come on,</i>
<i>spin and spin and spin!</i>

55:03.353 --> 55:08.256
<i>Oh, boy! Good ride, cowboy!</i>
<i>Well, let's see what</i>
<i>the judges say!</i>

55:08.458 --> 55:12.360
<i>I tell you, folks,</i>
<i>that sure looked like</i>
<i>the winnin' ride to me!</i>

55:30.912 --> 55:32.641
You know that girl?

55:33.482 --> 55:35.541
I sure do. Lureen Newsome.

55:35.951 --> 55:39.114
Her dad sells farm equipment.
I mean, big farm equipment.

55:39.187 --> 55:41.985
$100,000 tractors,
shit like that.

55:55.637 --> 55:58.731
What are you waitin' for,
cowboy? A matin' call?

