56:35.843 --> 56:39.836
# <i>No one's gonna love you</i>
<i>like me</i> #

56:41.248 --> 56:45.241
# <i>No one, no one</i> #

56:47.321 --> 56:51.553
# <i>I know</i>
<i>sometimes you felt</i> #

56:51.625 --> 56:55.561
# <i>So lonely</i> #

56:57.832 --> 56:59.800
# <i>I know</i> #

56:59.867 --> 57:04.099
# <i>You felt so sad and blue</i> ##

